</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-iLLNPL gTJAOY pf-71_"><strong>Resources are under pressure
</strong></h3><p class="sc-hGMjVM kxdODp pf-73_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-9ed0bd45-d45e-4f1d-a888-b6900f6f9f94"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Councils are expected to do more with less. That means automating compliance tasks, streamlining processes, and ensuring every resource is directed to where it can make the most impact.
</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-iLLNPL gTJAOY pf-76_"><strong>Accountability to communities
